---
const repo = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_GISCUS_REPO;
const repoId = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_GISCUS_REPO_ID;
const category = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_GISCUS_CATEGORY;
const categoryId = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_GISCUS_CATEGORY_ID;
const ready = repo && repoId && category && categoryId;
---

<section class="comments">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <p class="eyebrow">comments</p>
    <h2>留下几句话</h2>
    <p>评论区使用 GitHub Discussions 作为后端。若暂时没配好仓库，这里会先保持为空状态。</p>
  </div>

  {ready ? (
    <script is:inline src="https://giscus.app/client.js"
      data-repo={repo}
      data-repo-id={repoId}
      data-category={category}
      data-category-id={categoryId}
      data-mapping="pathname"
      data-strict="0"
      data-reactions-enabled="1"
      data-emit-metadata="0"
      data-input-position="bottom"
      data-theme="preferred_color_scheme"
      data-lang="zh-CN"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
      async>
    </script>
  ) : (
    <div class="comments__empty">
      <strong>评论尚未配置</strong>
      <p>
        把 `PUBLIC_GISCUS_REPO`、`PUBLIC_GISCUS_REPO_ID`、`PUBLIC_GISCUS_CATEGORY` 和
        `PUBLIC_GISCUS_CATEGORY_ID` 填进环境变量后，这里就会自动加载评论。
      </p>
    </div>
  )}
</section>
